<h2 class="api_method_name" data-subtopic="Conversations" name="method.conversations.add_recipients">
<a href="#method.conversations.add_recipients" name="method.conversations.add_recipients">
      Add recipients
    </a>
<span class="defined-in"><a href="https://github.com/instructure/canvas-lms/blob/master/app/controllers/conversations_controller.rb">ConversationsController#add_recipients</a></span>
</h2>
<h3 class="endpoint">
    POST /api/v1/conversations/:id/add_recipients
  </h3>
<p>Add recipients to an existing group conversation. Response is similar to
the GET/show action, except that only includes the latest message (e.g.
âjoe was added to the conversation by bobâ)</p>
