<td class="param-desc">
<p>An array of recipient ids. These may be user ids or course/group ids
prefixed with âcourse_â or âgroup_â respectively, e.g. <a href="">recipients[]=1&amp;recipients;</a>=2&amp;recipients[]=course_3</p>
